 enabling customers to deploy custom AI models ([azurecharts.com](https://azurecharts.com/updates?monthback=0)).\n\n---\n\n## 3. Strategic Cloud Investments in Japan to Scale Azure AI Infrastructure\n\n- Microsoft announced a **US\u202F$10\u202Fbillion investment** in Japan between 2026 and 2029 to build AI infrastructure, bolster cybersecurity, and train **one\u202Fmillion AI professionals by 2030** ([eweek.com](https://www.eweek.com/news/microsoft-10b-ai-investment-japan/)).\n\n- The initiative involves collaboration with SoftBank, Sakura Internet, NTT Data, NEC, Fujitsu, and Hitachi to develop localized compute capacity and support domestic AI model development ([cnbc.com](https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/03/sakura-internet-microsoft-ai-japan-softbank-investment.html)).\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\nIn summary, **today’s key updates** on Azure AI (as of April\u202F7,\u202F2026) include:\n\n- The release of powerful **new in-house MAI models** for transcription, voice, and image generation—**MAI‑Transcribe‑1**, **MAI‑Voice‑1**, and **MAI‑Image‑2**—now available to developers on Microsoft Foundry and MAI Playground.\n- Continued advancement of **agentic AI** across Microsoft’s product ecosystem, with new tools supporting autonomous task workflows and AI operations.\n- A major **strategic investment in Japan**, allocating US\u202F$10\u202Fbillion toward AI infrastructure, cybersecurity, and workforce development.\n\n---\n\nIf you'd like a deeper dive into any of these areas—such as pricing, technical specs, or deployment use cases—just let me know!","annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://techcrunch.com/2026/04/02/microsoft-takes-on-ai-rivals-with-three-new-foundational-models/","start_index":392,"end_index":510,"title":"Microsoft takes on AI rivals with three new foundational ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://microsoft.ai/news/today-were-announcing-3-new-world-class-mai-models-available-in-foundry/","start_index":788,"end_index":904,"title":"Today we're announcing 3 new world class MAI models, available in ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/azure-ai-foundry-blog/introducing-mai-transcribe-1-mai-voice-1-and-mai-image-2-in-microsoft-foundry/4507787","start_index":1150,"end_index":1331,"title":"Introducing MAI-Transcribe-1, MAI-Voice-1, and MAI-Image-2 in Microsoft ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/azure-ai-foundry-blog/introducing-mai-transcribe-1-mai-voice-1-and-mai-image-2-in-microsoft-foundry/4507787","start_index":1614,"end_index":1795,"title":"Introducing MAI-Transcribe-1, MAI-Voice-1, and MAI-Image-2 in Microsoft ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.theregister.com/2026/04/02/microsoft_models_homegrown_ai_models/","start_index":2014,"end_index":2111,"title":"Microsoft shivs OpenAI with new AI models for speech, images"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.geekwire.com/2026/microsoft-releases-new-ai-models-to-further-expand-beyond-openai/","start_index":2302,"end_index":2415,"title":"Microsoft releases new AI models to expand further beyond OpenAI"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://markets.financialcontent.com/stocks/article/marketminute-2026-4-3-microsoft-solidifies-enterprise-ai-dominance-as-agentic-era-triggers-software-re-rating","start_index":2832,"end_index":3027,"title":"Microsoft Solidifies Enterprise AI Dominance as 'Agentic' Era Triggers ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://azurecharts.com/updates?monthback=0","start_index":3223,"end_index":3287,"title":"Azure Updates in April 2026"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://azurecharts.com/updates?monthback=0","start_index":3423,"end_index":3487,"title":"Azure Updates in April 2026"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://azurecharts.com/updates?monthback=0","start_index":3610,"end_index":3674,"title":"Azure Updates in April 2026"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.eweek.com/news/microsoft-10b-ai-investment-japan/","start_index":3946,"end_index":4022,"title":"Microsoft Unveils $10B Plan to Scale AI, Cloud, and Cybersecurity in Japan"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/03/sakura-internet-microsoft-ai-japan-softbank-investment.html","start_index":4213,"end_index":4318,"title":"Japan's Sakura Internet jumps 20% as Microsoft plans $10 billion AI ..."}],"logprobs":[]}],"status":"completed"},"output_index":1,"sequence_number":87}

